  "body": [
    "Rajwinder Kaur is one of three siblings born to Sardar Kirpal Singh and Manjeet Kaur. Her parents noticed her interest in  music when she was at a tender age of four and supported her to pursue her interest. Her father and grandfather, Sardar Amar Singh, both have been musicians of fame in their own right. Rajwinder Kaur is a disciple of Rohit Ashav Bali Ji. Principal Sukhwant Singh of Jawaddi Taksal  is another mestro who has taught Rajwinder Kaur the fine nuances of music. She also fondly acknowledges the contribution of her college music teacher, Mrs. Heera Thukral. Both of Rajwinder’s sisters, Satnam Kaur and Satinder Kaur are accompanying artists who provide support in rhythm, strings and vocals."
